Goldwin Smith Hall

Ithaca, NY.

October 3, 1958

Dear Miss Loos,

My husband asks me to tell you that he was glad to autograph Lolita for you.

What comes now is a little embarrassing: he has been autographing Lolita only for personal friends and the very few writers whose work he admires. He has refused his autograph to so many of his own students and to so many of his acquaintances t